{"tid":99295,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(好正啊)Kristen Stewart show新紋身 原來跟執導的電影有關！","createTime":"2017-01-29T05:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T08:51:53.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9775f46a77e589371b1897e0e7285518f0d62cc","tid":99295,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5cefe3920.jpeg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5cefe3920.jpeg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d39017d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暮光女克莉絲汀史都華（Kristen Stewart），童星出身到接演暮光之城系列爆紅，可以說是許多粉絲關注的對象，而相當具有個性的她，現在又有新的導演身份，她所籌拍的短片《Come Swim》，即將在日舞影展上映，就連主題也相當前衛。<br />\n<br />\n▼暮光女克莉絲汀史都華（Kristen Stewart）兼具獨特的氣質也深獲許多品牌的青睞，沒想到除了演戲之外，她還相當具有才華，想要執導電影。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5cf0bab19.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5cf0bab19.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=eace8d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5cf16b7a5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5cf16b7a5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=b46edf53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼個人首次執導的短片《Come Swim》，即將在日舞影展首播，個人也接受媒體訪問，暢談創作理念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5c68eb204.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5c68eb204.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=bb7a5488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5c6427224.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5c6427224.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=64a7db42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20161118/large/1479468257_c1d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20161118%2Flarge%2F1479468257_c1d4.jpg&h=49ce70c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼而這部片來自她一直以來腦中的一個想法，她也特別把 Swim 字樣刺在手上變成後刺青。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62135/588d5c664e781.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62135%2F588d5c664e781.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=2f68aa0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荷里活演員許多在經過演戲的薰陶後，也發現自己有導演的能力，最值得一說的案例就是克林伊斯威特以及班&middot;艾佛列克了，如今暮光女也即將投入導演的一席，說不定也會闖出一片天。"},{"pid":"a5ccb56c86bf6a3f631a4ad4a495b673f070a45c","tid":99295,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T06:13:16.000Z","msg":"雖然做戲好屎 但佢真係好靚"},{"pid":"526b8b8f22d854d4d845cfcca47cf276ac59ed24","tid":99295,"uid":29987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"好有氣質<br />\n但無咩表情"}]}